{"id":369928,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":2}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"438","ytitle":"","mtitle":"鲜花送给小主人","ftitle":"","authors":["于之"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花儿香来鲜花儿红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花表达我们一片心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天是儿童的大喜日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花送给小主人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花儿香来鲜花儿红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给绿化近卫军:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处种下花和树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竖起万座新的长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"害虫害鸟消灭光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风风雨雨巡逻勤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国成了大花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千树万树绿成荫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军旗飘飘军纪严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保护着绿色小生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个见了不夸奖:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊，真像人民解放军!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花儿香来鲜花儿红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给除四害的小尖兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万双小手齐开火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭的敌人数不清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"校内校外讲卫生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把街道里弄扫干净。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每班都做小白鸽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不做那乌鸦黑妖精!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫生岗站在街头喊:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“别随地吐痰传病菌!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路人纷纷在夸奖:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“多像当年小民兵!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花儿香来鲜花儿红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给勤劳的好学生:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习成绩质量高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不出两分没废品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天练习普通话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推广运动中当先锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比小小火车头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把全市的舌头都带动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁在田头教文化?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是下乡扫盲的红领巾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔阿姨都夸奖:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“多么能干的小先生!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花儿香来鲜花儿红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花送给小英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给工农兵的小助手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给毛泽东的好儿童。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们像鲜花迎风开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们像绿苗长成林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一同大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来的世界属于我们!"}]}